spec_data.Name: dh-make
spec_data.Description:
This package allows you to take a standard (or upstream) source
package and convert it into a format that will allow you to build
Debian packages.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 03:44:28 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Tool that converts source archives into Debian package source
